This project uses `AGENTS.md` as the AI workflow entry point with programmatic enforcement.

Read `AGENTS.md` for complete workflow instructions.
Read `.agents/rules/workflow_rules.md` for mandatory enforcement rules.

Critical rules:
- Before writing code: run `agent phase status`.
- Before planning: run `agent validate planning`.
- Before release: run `agent decision`.
- Register risks with `agent risk add <severity> <description>`.
- Use `agent repair start` for QA-driven repair loops.
- Do not skip phases or ignore blocked results.
- All user-facing conversation must be in Chinese.
